text: Onward is a 2020 American computer-animated urban fantasy comedy movie produced by Pixar Animation Studios for Walt Disney Pictures. The movie is directed by Dan Scanlon. It stars Tom Holland, Chris Pratt, Julia Louis- Dreyfus, and Octavia Spencer. It is set in a suburban fantasy world. The movie is about two elf brothers who go out on a journey to find an artifact that will bring back their father. The movie was released in the United States on March 6, 2020. It had positive reviews from critics but did not make a lot of money because of the 2019â€“20 coronavirus pandemic.
